<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TKT11">
<l>toṇṭellām paravi niṉṉait toḻutaṭi paṇiyu māṟu</l>
<l>kaṇṭutāṉ kavalai tīrppā ṉāvatē paṇiyā yentāy</l>
<l>aṇṭamā yeṇṭi caikku mātiyāy nīti yāṉa</l>
<l>paṇṭamām parama cōti niṉṉaiyē paravu vēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Grant that one ends [one’s] sorrows, my father, having seen the way</l>
<l>Of prostrating at [your] feet, worshipping you, [and] praising [you with] all [forms of] service;</l>
<l>As the universe, as the source for the eight directions,</l>
<l>Highest Light that is wealth which is upright, I praise only you.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
